pare time. He and Mrs. Thomas have </div><div class="t m249 xa h27 y89a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">two adult children. </div><div class="t m7e7 x5b h8c y3c5 ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check with your local Adventist Book </div><div class="t m607 x5b h8c y1346 ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Center for the companion book to the </div><div class="t m2c6 x5b h8c y590 ff4 fs31 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
